	  <b>          
	    <i>          
	      Milestones
	    </i>          
	  </b>          
	</p>          
	<p style="font-size:130%; text-align:center">          
	  One huge part of the game will be the global counter milestones. For example, if the community gets the counter to 10,000, then something new would be added to the game.
